title: For Sale/Trade:  AK SlideFire Stock (Right hand)
postcontent: Will trade for 5.56, 223, 9mm, 357, Quality bipod, highend brand name tactical light, cheap .22 rifles/pistols, I can add cash on my end if needed to square a deal. The Slide Fire Solutions SSAK-47 XRS Bump Fire Buttstock utilizes the same groundbreaking design and technology as the SSAR-15 line of stocks, offering the same level of performance, reliability, and superior craftsmanship for the more economical AK-47 platform of rifles. The SSAK-47 allows the shooter to safely bump fire their AKM-pattern rifle from the shoulder, effectively and legally simulating fully automatic fire, and allowing for an unprecedented measure of control that is severely lacking when attempting to bump fire a rifle in the traditional, "from-the-hip" manner. The SSAK-47 features a shelf that positions the shooter's index finger in a fixed position in front of the rifle's trigger. To fire, the rifle is moved forward with the support hand pushing on the forend, thereby bringing the trigger to the shooter's finger and discharging a round. The rifle's recoil causes it to move rearward, allowing the trigger mechanism to reset. When the right amount of constant forward pressure is applied, the rifle will continue to fire as the trigger is brought forward and depressed by the shooter's stationary index finger, causing the gun to Bump Fire. With a little practice, the shooter will be capable of delivering accurate single shots, bursts, or even full magazine dumps on demand using the SSAK-47. The SSAK-47 employs a simple stock locking mechanism that allows shooters to select between their preferred firing methods easily and quickly. In the extended or "Open" position, the rifle's receiver is allowed to freely slide rearward during the recoil impulse into the hollow stock, thereby allowing the gun to be bump fired. The stock may also be locked into a collapsed, or "Closed," position into which the Interface Block attached the gun's receiver is held in place within the hollow stock and unable to move, thereby facilitating semi-auto function. The SSAK-47 is designed to be compatible with most Stamped Receiver, Fixed Stock AK-47 and AK-74 rifle variants, as well as Saiga Rifles and Shotguns that have been converted from their imported sporting configurations to accept a pistol grip. Stock is NOT compatible with Milled Receiver rifles or those with Underfolding or Side-Folding buttstocks. No permanent modifications or gunsmithing required! SSAK-47 assembly includes the XRS Stock, Interface Block, Nut Retainer, Hex Key, Mounting Hardware, Instructions, BATFE Approval Letter, and a Lifetime Factory Warranty. Made in the USA. Technical Information:Model: SSAK-47 XRSStock Material: Reinforced High Strength PolymerCompatibility: Stamped Receiver, Fixed Stock AK-47/AK-74 variants, Converted Saiga Rifles & ShotgunsNOTE: The Left Hand Model has a fixed finger shelf located on the right side of the stock. The trigger will be blocked by this shelf and inaccessible when fired with the right hand.The Right Hand Model has a fixed finger shelf located on the left side of the stock. The trigger will be blocked by this shelf and inaccessible when fired with the left hand.
